n: Peanut Butter and Pimento Cheese-Stuffed Celery
des: "My grandmother had these at the holiday table every year, and I continue to pass it down through my family! We love it!"
ins: Spread peanut butter into one half of the hollow in each celery stalk. Spread pimento cheese spread into the other half. Refrigerate until chilled, at least 20 minutes.
